{"tid":1795551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北美防空司令部啟動超級任務","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T04:54:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"115e569131d64338b955dab8cb5b751dc67f722b","tid":1795551,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/12/1-417-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1-417-800x450.jpg&h=bdce0d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（<a href=\"http://圖取自facebook.com/noradsanta）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAfacebook.com%2Fnoradsanta%EF%BC%89&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=44777c23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自facebook.com/noradsanta）</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節將至，美國國防部23日上午正式宣布，北美防空司令部的聖誕老人追蹤計劃正式啟動，大小朋友都能夠透過網路，知道聖誕老人正在哪片天空發送禮物。<br />\n<br />\n追蹤聖誕老人計劃在美國國防部已經進行超過60年，負責追蹤飛越北美與周邊地區飛行物的北美防空司令部（NORAD）今年也依循傳統繼續「追蹤聖誕老人、馴鹿和他的神奇雪橇」。<br />\n<br />\n北美防空司令部不僅開放大小朋友透過 <a href=\"http://NORADSanta.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNORADSanta.org&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=e3e48303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">NORADSanta.org</a> 平台追蹤聖誕老人的行蹤，也會接聽來自全球兒童電話。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部是如何擔起這個「追蹤聖誕老人」的計劃呢？在1955年聖誕前夕，美國「科羅拉多斯普林斯新聞報」（Colorado Springs Newspaper）刊登一則邀請小朋友致電聖誕老人的廣告中，竟將電話號碼置為北美防空司令部指揮中心電話，當時讓北美防空司令部的平安夜因電話鈴聲不斷而不得寧靜。<br />\n<br />\n但為了不讓打來電話的小朋友失望，北美防空司令部不僅認真回覆孩子們的來電，也向小朋友提供聖誕老人的位置。<br />\n<br />\n64年來，北美防空司令部持續在聖誕前夕啟動聖誕老人追蹤計畫，讓大小朋友可以在平安夜追蹤聖誕老人行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/12/24/a102736328.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F12%2F24%2Fa102736328.html&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=98713c5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/12/24/a102736328.html</a>"},{"pid":"347d1466ec96a3479e0cd12d4c29bbe2702ec412","tid":1795551,"uid":55010,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"好正，啲軍人同你玩埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸既話啲細路死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432c34aa59ab08478314be44abeed935d9c7865c","tid":1795551,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20150205/HK/_05BU003_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20150205%2FHK%2F_05BU003_.jpg&h=23f917f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181218/640_68593f486a097cdfd3edae6b14e7bae1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181218%2F640_68593f486a097cdfd3edae6b14e7bae1.jpg&h=d0e94659&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bda4ee85edb2ace23798590c162d0dfc10797fc","tid":1795551,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sir, this way.<br />\n<br />\nFive demands, Not one less<br />\n<br />\nEmail已sent <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nnoradtrackssanta@outlook.com</span>"},{"pid":"22a6b4817acc8d73579bc07eef08951de1ea4e57","tid":1795551,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"去北京給小男孩送禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee093ad2e504ce37d11de5d92bfb27a65ea0ff3","tid":1795551,"uid":9338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"22a6b4817acc8d73579bc07eef08951de1ea4e57","tid":1795551,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"去北京給小男孩送禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/